<td class="plainlist" style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em;font-weight:bold;border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;">
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Outline_of_Buddhism" title="Outline of Buddhism">Outline</a></li>
<li><span class="metadata"><a href="/wiki/File:Dharma_Wheel.svg" class="image"><img alt="Portal icon" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Dharma_Wheel.svg/16px-Dharma_Wheel.svg.png" width="16" height="16" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Dharma_Wheel.svg/24px-Dharma_Wheel.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/df/Dharma_Wheel.svg/32px-Dharma_Wheel.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="690" data-file-height="690" /></a></span> <a href="/wiki/Portal:Buddhism" title="Portal:Buddhism">Buddhism portal</a></li>
